      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali, from his father, from Al Nowfaly, from Al Sakuny, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Rasool-Allah<sup>saww</sup> said: ‘Do Jihad, you would acquire’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "14. Ali has narrated from father, from al-Nawfaliy from al-Sakuniy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that the Messenger of Allah has said, ‘You must do Jihad; you will benefit.’” "
        ]
      }
